Okay I found a workaround, package.json config in browserList wasn't the same in prod and dev, in prod. It was : ```   "browserslist": {
    "production": [
      ">0.2%",
      "not dead",
      "not op_mini all"
    ],
    "development": [
      "last 1 chrome version",
      "last 1 firefox version",
      "last 1 safari version"
    ]
  }
```
I changed it to :
```  "browserslist": {
    "production": [
      "defaults"
    ],
    "development": [
      "defaults"
    ]
  }```
